1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,740
The nearest star to Earth is four light years away.

2
00:00:02,740 --> 00:00:04,140
Sounds close, right?

3
00:00:04,140 --> 00:00:05,200
Here's the catch.

4
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:07,380
Our fastest spacecraft, aimed straight at it,

5
00:00:07,380 --> 00:00:09,340
wouldn't take hundreds of years to get there.

6
00:00:09,340 --> 00:00:11,980
It would take 77,000 years.

7
00:00:11,980 --> 00:00:13,300
And that's just the first problem

8
00:00:13,300 --> 00:00:14,740
with ever meeting an alien.
